data.meta_description: I was reading a magazine with an article about a kenpo "master" named thomas mitose who claims that his late father, grandmaster of a style of kenpo, was a freind of o-sensei and calims that o-sensei said in his will and testament that mitose's father should be promoted to 10th dan aikido and proclaimed remonstrant of aikido in the west. is this all true?
